Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一．起．来．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.49,0:01:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那天以来的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都希望能感觉的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.37,0:01:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管到哪里都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.44,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管做什么都好让人心动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷入恋爱的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都好像魔法师一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以让人高兴起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
