Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧\N一起来吧 一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大胆!被抱了好高兴喔!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轻轻地...轻轻地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.07,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~就差一点点了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，开门的时要轻一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，看的出来是我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，再来要玩什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿\N干爹A不是刚刚才说过了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，这样还看得出是我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿该不会是想让我们吓一跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么看都有那个意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会不会是友纪不在，觉得很寂寞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再来的话，不管是什么打扮\N我们都装作很吃惊的样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想看莉采儿高兴的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了 准备好了吗?\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你、你是什么人啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑的家伙，难道是哪里派来\N想抢走可爱的莉采儿的间谍吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，看你那脸就知道一定是这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃...别把刚洗的衣服给弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,积了很多好不容易才洗完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么看都是莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.36,0:04:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，这太明显了啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锵~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~没有人发现耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉、莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真、真是吓了我们一跳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到会是莉采儿呢...对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全没有发现呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是、是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，这样就没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，慢走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心车子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说要出去\N那副打扮是要到哪儿去啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一提...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一提...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我老公买来\N要在宴会上戴的鼻眼镜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事无所谓啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了到了\N可是我现在并不是莉采儿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听好了，小汪汪\N我是莉采儿这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要对老公保密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.20,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~学校是这么大的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样要找老公可辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去喽，喔~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为如此\N这里会变成这样再变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所求得的答案就变成这样，不过...\N大家都懂了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.45,0:06:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~ 老公~\N你在哪里啊~ 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.16,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃...啊...嗯...\N那时候，就光源氏的心境来说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点出来呀\N老公啊~ 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最帅气的老公啊~ 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀哎呀你是在哪里啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.24,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最爱的老老老老老公啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里一个人也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.27,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就叫好戏在后头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待会讲的地方考试会考出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要东张西望的，给我好好听课!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.88,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么\N我非得学这些早就知道的东西不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是无聊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.59,0:07:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不在这里\N老公你到底在哪里嘛...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走路时不看好前面还真不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?眼镜眼镜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，有了有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太可爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那名可爱的少女是谁啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变装变装...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那...那个是...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.19,0:07:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小、小、小熊...内、内...\N我说不出口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!我身为一个绅士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎能偷窥少女的内...\N那白色的东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，真是位可爱的少女啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一次有好好看前面了说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起这个\N要快点找到老公才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿，三年B班的同学们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到教室以前都还是校外教学呢\N队伍不要乱掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会断了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了，岩城同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?没什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚你盯着老师在发呆吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真不死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开玩笑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去...
