Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一群无情的家伙...嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里面的情形似乎有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.05,0:09:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我进去看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要~!救救我，老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.33,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救我啊，老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在搞什么啊，莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对!你是谁啊\N我又不是莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快踩煞车，煞车啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是叫你踩煞车了吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么是煞车啊~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连煞车都不知道就不要骑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来!停下来!\N可是停不下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停不下来也没关系\N就别再跑了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么那家伙会来学校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要撞上了，不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快不行了啦~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样来不及的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，要撞上了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.76,0:10:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...是你救了我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是第一次被老公救耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点也不好笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么啊\N骑着车跑来跑去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.15,0:10:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家想说骑那个的话\N就可以快一点找到老公了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁要你来找我啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要自作主张，你这白痴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家费了不少苦心的说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂、别哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等、等一下\N想在这里搞爆炸啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，要哭了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，我知道了啦\N总之别哭啊，莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撑不住了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~真是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个应该是B班的岩城同学吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他跟那个少女是什么关系啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭，还不能哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还不能放炸弹啊!\N不要哭，莉采儿!
