Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里不行啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不能让它爆炸啊，莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的话...
