Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就不行啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐~怎么到哪\N都有人冒出来啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公从刚才就一直抱着我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这妻子是多么的幸福啊\N老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.99,0:12:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧了\N我已经不会想哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得被我最喜欢的老公抱着\N怎么可以哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊，都回到家啦
