Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
